com.polarion.alm.tracker.model.signatures

Interface IDocumentWorkflowSignature

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAdaptable, IChangeListener, IHasValues, IPObject, IUniqueObject, IWorkflowSignature

    public interface IDocumentWorkflowSignature
extends IWorkflowSignature
    Document workflow signature represents a signature for one transition to a workflow status of a document.
    Since:
    3.9.0
    See Also:
    IWorkflowSignature

      • getTransitionRevision

        @Nullable
java.lang.String getTransitionRevision()
        Revision of the parent object in which the workflow transition was performed, or null if the transition was not performed yet. If the signature is branched from another document, the transition revision will be of the source document.
        Specified by:
        getTransitionRevision in interface IWorkflowSignature

      • getBranchedFrom

        @Nullable
IDocumentWorkflowSignature getBranchedFrom()
        The signature of which this workflow signature is a branch. If filled, getWorkflowObject() is a document branched from getBranchedFrom() and the signature was created before branching and was copied to this document as this signature.
